snippet.textDisplay: I know this is top hits list, but have you heard any tracks off of Trench by twenty one pilots? It's definitely a step up from their more poppy stuff from the Blurryface era (I still love that album but it's definitely way too typical pop music). But Trench I genuine believe they were able to pull off a truly great experimental pop album. It's worth a listen if you havent already. Tracks like Morph and Chlorine are just so groovy and catchy, I still listen to them on a nearly daily basis.
